WEBVTT



00:00:21.519 --> 00:00:24.839
I called Xiaoliang,
but he didn't answer.

00:00:25.179 --> 00:00:26.839
Xiaoliang won't be implicated.

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:31.039
I'll get you out of Beiyan first,
and then go get him.

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:32.859
We'll find a chance to meet up.

00:00:34.420 --> 00:00:35.700
It's all my fault.

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:39.920
Qin, don't say that.

00:00:42.500 --> 00:00:46.060
Fortune favors the bold.
This is the price to pay

00:00:46.899 --> 00:00:48.399
to change our fate.

00:01:00.100 --> 00:01:00.719
Hello.

00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:11.019
If I don't see you,

00:01:12.719 --> 00:01:14.280
I'll go crazy.

00:01:16.680 --> 00:01:20.939
Otherwise, I'll spill
all your dirty secrets.

00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:24.260
East Suburb abandoned factory.
Meet me there.

00:01:25.579 --> 00:01:26.299
Don't cry!

00:01:46.719 --> 00:01:47.680
Turn the car around.

00:01:48.439 --> 00:01:50.799
Qin, leave this to me. I'll go find him.

00:01:51.760 --> 00:01:53.400
Huang Mantang is after me.

00:01:53.579 --> 00:01:56.540
If he doesn't see me,
he'll definitely call the cops.

00:01:56.540 --> 00:01:58.980
Qin, I can handle him.
You just take Xiaoliang and go.

00:01:58.980 --> 00:02:01.540
No! Xiaoliang can't know.

00:02:02.579 --> 00:02:03.939
I can't take that risk.

00:02:05.500 --> 00:02:06.079
Turn around.

00:03:20.954 --> 00:03:24.026
=The Silent Rift=

00:03:24.314 --> 00:03:26.906
=Episode 14=
(Revenge Gone Mad)

00:03:27.620 --> 00:03:28.520
- Officer Zhu!
- Li Fen.

00:03:28.520 --> 00:03:29.620
You're finally here!

00:03:29.659 --> 00:03:31.319
I couldn't find her anywhere.

00:03:31.319 --> 00:03:32.620
- Chuchu is well-behaved.
- Calm.

00:03:32.620 --> 00:03:33.580
- She would never wander off.
- Calm down.

00:03:33.580 --> 00:03:35.659
What happened? Tell me slowly.

00:03:36.219 --> 00:03:38.099
I-I brought my daughter here to shop.

00:03:38.240 --> 00:03:40.319
When I was paying,
I turned around, and she was gone.

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:42.400
I-I just found her doll
on the floor here.

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:44.759
Don't panic. You need to stay calm.

00:03:48.379 --> 00:03:49.159
Stay calm.

00:03:49.740 --> 00:03:51.860
I'll have a colleague pull
the surveillance footage.

00:03:52.659 --> 00:03:54.939
We'll know what happened
in the past two hours soon.

00:03:55.740 --> 00:03:57.159
(Grocery Section)
In the next 24 hours,

00:03:57.659 --> 00:03:58.819
someone will be with you.

00:03:59.300 --> 00:04:03.460
If you get a call for ransom,

00:04:04.360 --> 00:04:06.319
just answer it.
My colleague will be with you.

00:04:07.740 --> 00:04:08.879
Did you check the back door?

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:09.520
No.

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.120
Li Fen.

00:04:15.939 --> 00:04:17.740
It is important for you
to stay calm now.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:18.800
Think carefully.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:21.240
Have you encountered anyone
or anything unusual recently?

00:04:21.800 --> 00:04:22.379
No.

00:04:22.819 --> 00:04:23.959
Think hard.

00:04:40.139 --> 00:04:41.000
I know.

00:04:42.500 --> 00:04:43.279
It's him.

00:04:43.500 --> 00:04:45.720
Xue Yonghui must have recognized me.

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:47.540
He's afraid I'll testify against him.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:50.660
He took Chuchu. He's trying
to blackmail me, Officer Zhu.

00:04:50.939 --> 00:04:52.560
Explain yourself. What do you mean?

00:04:53.639 --> 00:04:55.000
One of the credit union robbers

00:04:55.879 --> 00:04:57.600
was Xue Yonghui.

00:04:59.100 --> 00:05:00.319
Are you telling the truth?

00:05:00.500 --> 00:05:02.639
The welfare factory belongs to Caisheng,

00:05:03.100 --> 00:05:05.000
but we have little business interaction.

00:05:05.160 --> 00:05:08.220
My impression of him was just a name.

00:05:09.439 --> 00:05:12.500
When I saw him that day,
I recognized his eyes.

00:05:13.279 --> 00:05:15.480
I kept wondering why
those eyes looked so familiar.

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:16.939
I just couldn't place it.

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:20.980
But I'm sure that those eyes
were definitely his.

00:05:20.980 --> 00:05:24.560
Xue Yonghui kidnapped Chuchu.
It has to be him, Officer Zhu.

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:26.540
What's our next move?

00:05:26.779 --> 00:05:28.720
If Xue Yonghui kidnapped Chuchu,

00:05:29.639 --> 00:05:32.160
he must be prepared
to fight to the death now.

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:34.160
Li Fen, come on.

00:05:35.560 --> 00:05:36.639
Someone called the cops,

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:39.800
saying Xue Yonghui is holding hostages
at the East Suburb abandoned factory.

00:05:42.500 --> 00:05:43.339
Who was the caller?

00:05:43.379 --> 00:05:44.339
He wouldn't say.

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:47.720
He said there's a show waiting for us.

00:05:48.100 --> 00:05:48.660
Let's go.

00:06:06.939 --> 00:06:07.500
Qin.

00:06:11.139 --> 00:06:11.920
Watch your step.

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:21.939
Chuchu?

00:06:23.660 --> 00:06:24.220
Qin.

00:06:32.639 --> 00:06:33.279
Careful, Qin.

00:06:35.060 --> 00:06:35.839
Yonghui!

00:06:43.226 --> 00:06:44.288
(Zhu Helai)

00:06:51.418 --> 00:06:53.280
(Zhu Helai)

00:06:53.939 --> 00:06:54.779
Hello? What is it?

00:06:55.560 --> 00:06:57.279
On a call right now. Talk later.

00:06:57.639 --> 00:06:59.339
Xue Yonghui is extremely dangerous.

00:06:59.639 --> 00:07:00.319
What did you say?

00:07:00.660 --> 00:07:02.139
He was involved in the 6.10 robbery.

00:07:02.500 --> 00:07:05.220
He's highly likely to have
kidnapped Li Fen's daughter by now.

00:07:05.639 --> 00:07:07.939
Arrest Xue Yonghui immediately!

00:07:09.939 --> 00:07:10.720
Got it.

00:07:11.139 --> 00:07:12.160
Is that it?

00:07:12.500 --> 00:07:13.319
Zhu Helai.

00:07:13.939 --> 00:07:14.939
Listen. This isn't

00:07:14.939 --> 00:07:16.339
just about you.

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:17.540
We'll talk later.

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:47.720
Qin, now that things have come to this,

00:07:48.379 --> 00:07:50.379
can you tell me

00:07:51.319 --> 00:07:53.220
whose child Xiaoliang is?

00:07:54.500 --> 00:07:57.379
Is Xiaoliang our child?

00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.779
Just tell me.

00:08:03.354 --> 00:08:05.560
(Magou Town, Video Theater)

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:06.920
Don't think I'm some easy woman.

00:08:07.439 --> 00:08:09.220
I'm not that kind
of shallow, vain woman.

00:08:10.160 --> 00:08:11.100
Stay back!

00:08:34.659 --> 00:08:35.539
Take care.

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:42.059
Why not leave, Mantang?

00:08:44.159 --> 00:08:45.100
Haven't eaten yet?

00:08:49.639 --> 00:08:51.840
Want some? It's still warm.

00:08:51.840 --> 00:08:52.340
Here.

00:08:53.899 --> 00:08:54.519
Eat up.

00:08:56.399 --> 00:08:57.159
Eat up.

00:09:02.159 --> 00:09:03.279
Look at this mess.

00:09:59.899 --> 00:10:01.200
Just let us go.

00:10:07.159 --> 00:10:08.840
You're still protecting him?

00:10:10.139 --> 00:10:14.139
Fine. Meng Guangcai
is scared of Zhu Helai, right?

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:17.460
Well, I've called Zhu Helai
and his team over today.

00:10:18.659 --> 00:10:20.639
I'm doing something big today.

00:10:21.519 --> 00:10:22.639
You just wait.

00:10:35.720 --> 00:10:36.399
Mr. Yonghui.

00:10:37.399 --> 00:10:40.139
You should've seen this coming.

00:10:40.960 --> 00:10:42.080
Let me tell you.

00:10:42.840 --> 00:10:46.960
If I didn't want someone upset,
I'd kill you a thousand times.

00:10:47.899 --> 00:10:49.840
You've beaten me so many times.

00:10:51.399 --> 00:10:52.519
Stop!

00:10:54.659 --> 00:10:56.399
Huang Mantang, stop!

00:10:58.019 --> 00:10:59.519
You made me bark like a dog!

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:00.460
Yonghui!

00:11:00.460 --> 00:11:01.779
You made me act like a dog!

00:11:03.460 --> 00:11:04.519
You made me do it!

00:11:05.460 --> 00:11:06.840
Yonghui!

00:11:07.840 --> 00:11:08.899
Help!

00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:16.700
You wanted to be crippled, didn't you?

00:11:17.460 --> 00:11:19.460
I'll make sure both
your hands are useless.

00:11:21.519 --> 00:11:22.759
Yonghui.

00:12:15.080 --> 00:12:17.580
Chai Daqing, you're surrounded.

00:12:18.700 --> 00:12:21.659
Stay calm. Whatever it is,
we can talk it out.

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:24.820
Just one condition.
You must keep the hostages safe.

00:12:25.279 --> 00:12:28.519
Zhu Helai! Get Zhu Helai
here to talk to me.

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:33.779
Okay, we'll try our best
to let Zhu Helai come.

00:12:33.779 --> 00:12:35.279
But you must stay calm.

00:12:38.580 --> 00:12:39.340
Chai Daqing.

00:12:40.279 --> 00:12:42.899
I'm Zhu Helai's superior.

00:12:43.340 --> 00:12:45.700
My name is Liu Hua.
Please don't get agitated.

00:12:46.220 --> 00:12:49.399
I'll try to meet any request
you have, okay?

00:12:49.399 --> 00:12:52.840
Get lost! What superior?
Go get Zhu Helai!

00:12:53.399 --> 00:12:54.340
Tell him,

00:12:54.899 --> 00:12:57.139
isn't he dying to know about
the truth of the 6.10 case?

00:12:57.460 --> 00:12:59.840
If he doesn't come, I won't say a word.

00:13:00.139 --> 00:13:00.779
Alright.

00:13:01.519 --> 00:13:03.159
Don't get agitated. I agree, okay?

00:13:03.519 --> 00:13:05.519
Just a moment. Give me some time.

00:13:06.460 --> 00:13:09.139
Zhang Wei. Go get Zhu Helai.

00:13:11.399 --> 00:13:12.779
Zhang Wei, go ahead.

00:13:15.340 --> 00:13:16.200
Okay, got it.

00:13:19.639 --> 00:13:22.460
Snipers, listen up!
Ensure the hostages' safety.

00:13:30.279 --> 00:13:34.340
He fathered a child with someone else,
yet you still protect him?

00:13:35.080 --> 00:13:36.700
He has to die today.

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:39.080
He has to die today.

00:13:41.960 --> 00:13:42.639
Chuchu.

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:45.539
- Chuchu.
- Ma'am, you can't go in.

00:13:45.539 --> 00:13:46.840
- Chu...
- Let go of me!

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:47.580
- Can't go in.
- Let go!

00:13:47.580 --> 00:13:48.200
- Can't go in.
- Master.

00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:49.100
- Let go!
- Calm down.

00:13:49.100 --> 00:13:51.460
- Ma'am.
- Calm her down.

00:13:51.460 --> 00:13:52.340
- Zhu.
- Chuchu.

00:13:52.340 --> 00:13:53.139
Chuchu.

00:13:53.340 --> 00:13:55.340
Going in now
will only agitate the suspect,

00:13:55.340 --> 00:13:56.399
endangering Chuchu.

00:13:56.639 --> 00:13:58.200
The suspect's emotions aren't stable.

00:13:58.200 --> 00:13:59.899
When you go in, focus on two things.

00:13:59.960 --> 00:14:02.519
First, guarantee hostages' safety.
Second, guarantee your safety.

00:14:02.519 --> 00:14:03.200
- Okay?
- Okay.

00:14:03.200 --> 00:14:04.519
Here, put on the protective gear.

00:14:04.519 --> 00:14:05.200
Here, Master.

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:05.960
I'm not wearing it.

00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:08.520
The suspect might get agitated
seeing it. Better avoid it.

00:14:08.840 --> 00:14:09.840
Are the hostages safe?

00:14:09.840 --> 00:14:10.519
Yes.

00:14:11.279 --> 00:14:11.899
Testing.

00:14:12.139 --> 00:14:13.580
Testing, one, two, three.

00:14:13.580 --> 00:14:14.279
Okay, copy that.

00:14:16.960 --> 00:14:17.720
I'm going in.

00:14:18.960 --> 00:14:21.580
Chai Daqing, Zhu Helai is coming now.

00:14:21.840 --> 00:14:24.340
He's unarmed. Don't get agitated.

00:14:36.639 --> 00:14:37.639
Snipers, standby.

00:14:37.899 --> 00:14:38.399
Copy that.

00:14:40.200 --> 00:14:42.460
Zhu, you're here.

00:14:43.019 --> 00:14:44.019
Just stay there.

00:14:45.399 --> 00:14:48.779
You called me over in such a hurry.
I wonder what it's about.

00:14:49.399 --> 00:14:50.700
Chai Daqing. No.

00:14:52.639 --> 00:14:54.460
Should I call you Huang Mantang?

00:14:56.019 --> 00:14:56.960
Exactly, Zhu.

00:14:57.840 --> 00:15:01.659
Haven't met for over ten years.
I'm surprised you recognize me.

00:15:01.720 --> 00:15:03.139
Of course, Mantang.

00:15:04.279 --> 00:15:06.639
You've changed completely
since you were little.

00:15:06.639 --> 00:15:09.279
You seem much sharper now than before.

00:15:09.720 --> 00:15:11.659
No wonder no one recognized you.

00:15:11.960 --> 00:15:14.460
And they all thought you were dead.

00:15:14.899 --> 00:15:18.200
They made me play dead,
and set up a fake grave for me.

00:15:18.779 --> 00:15:19.779
And you all bought it?

00:15:20.399 --> 00:15:21.779
You rushed to get me here.

00:15:22.840 --> 00:15:24.399
Is there something you want to tell me?

00:15:24.580 --> 00:15:27.779
Are you dying to know about
the truth of the 6.10 case?

00:15:27.840 --> 00:15:28.460
Mantang.

00:15:29.519 --> 00:15:31.159
If you tell me about the 6.10 case,

00:15:32.159 --> 00:15:33.340
I am all ears.

00:15:34.159 --> 00:15:36.899
We have plenty of time. Take it slow.

00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:40.840
I'll listen carefully
to every word you say.

00:15:41.519 --> 00:15:42.580
But put the knife down.

00:15:42.580 --> 00:15:43.220
Don't move!

00:15:44.139 --> 00:15:45.399
You'd better not move.

00:15:45.960 --> 00:15:47.659
You letting me come over

00:15:48.279 --> 00:15:50.220
proves you still have some remorse.

00:15:50.700 --> 00:15:52.639
If you show willingness to surrender,

00:15:52.639 --> 00:15:55.399
I will definitely help you
get leniency. Okay?

00:15:56.840 --> 00:16:00.700
I'm a dying man.
What use is leniency to me?

00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:03.460
I want to see Meng Xiaoliang!

00:16:03.700 --> 00:16:04.340
Okay.

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:07.080
Meng Xiaoliang will come.

00:16:07.580 --> 00:16:09.460
I have so much to say to Xiaoliang.

00:16:10.960 --> 00:16:14.159
I've called all you police here today

00:16:14.519 --> 00:16:16.340
to be my witnesses.

00:16:17.139 --> 00:16:19.720
I'm going to do something great.

00:16:20.019 --> 00:16:22.399
I'll tell you everything they've done.

00:16:22.580 --> 00:16:25.639
I want them to die and join me in death!

00:16:25.659 --> 00:16:26.700
Calm down, Mantang.

00:16:27.779 --> 00:16:29.139
My time is running out.

00:16:30.580 --> 00:16:33.700
This brat... This brat has to die!

00:16:33.700 --> 00:16:34.720
Mantang, calm down.

00:16:35.580 --> 00:16:38.460
I will remove all obstacles
for Meng Xiaoliang.

00:16:39.139 --> 00:16:42.460
I will make Meng Xiaoliang inherit
all of Meng Guangcai's money.

00:16:43.139 --> 00:16:44.779
All of Meng Guangcai's property.

00:16:49.279 --> 00:16:51.639
Zhu, tell Meng Guangcai

00:16:52.460 --> 00:16:55.019
that what I take from him today

00:16:55.399 --> 00:16:56.580
is everything he has.

00:16:58.340 --> 00:16:59.200
He'll understand.

00:17:01.580 --> 00:17:02.399
Zhu,

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:06.160
you want to know
the truth of the 6.10 case, right?

00:17:06.460 --> 00:17:07.400
I'll tell you.

00:17:08.079 --> 00:17:09.160
That day, the four of us...

00:17:12.779 --> 00:17:13.400
Watch out!

00:17:15.180 --> 00:17:15.680
Shoot!

00:17:17.700 --> 00:17:18.279
Master!

00:17:18.880 --> 00:17:19.759
Save the hostages.

00:17:19.759 --> 00:17:20.440
Master!

00:17:20.440 --> 00:17:21.660
Save the hostages! Hurry!

00:17:22.079 --> 00:17:22.700
Huang Mantang!

00:17:22.700 --> 00:17:23.279
Chuchu!

00:17:23.279 --> 00:17:24.079
- Mom!
- Huang Mantang, tell me

00:17:24.079 --> 00:17:25.400
if Meng Guangcai was involved?

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:27.140
Was he involved in the case 6.10?

00:17:27.140 --> 00:17:27.819
Huang Mantang!

00:17:29.640 --> 00:17:30.920
Yonghui!

00:17:31.420 --> 00:17:32.779
Mom!

00:17:33.200 --> 00:17:33.920
Huang Mantang!

00:17:35.200 --> 00:17:36.559
Yonghui!

00:17:37.680 --> 00:17:39.039
Yonghui!

00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:42.559
Yonghui!

00:17:44.579 --> 00:17:45.640
Yonghui!

00:18:07.400 --> 00:18:08.640
(Suspects)
I only realize now

00:18:09.220 --> 00:18:14.440
that Xue Yonghui decided to kill after getting
Meng Guangcai's noodle-eating signal.

00:18:15.799 --> 00:18:17.559
Who was most worthy of being killed?

00:18:18.799 --> 00:18:22.299
It was this one who just
appeared but was silenced,

00:18:24.059 --> 00:18:25.680
Meng Xiaoliang's biological dad.

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:28.680
This Huang Mantang
who had already died once.

00:18:50.319 --> 00:18:52.960
Mom, go back to your room and rest.

00:18:54.900 --> 00:18:56.539
I'm afraid I'll miss the call.

00:18:57.799 --> 00:18:59.920
If you're hungry,
have the housekeeper make you food.

00:19:02.039 --> 00:19:05.819
Mom, wasn't that man Uncle's driver?

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:08.420
Why did he kidnap you?

00:19:09.700 --> 00:19:11.319
Why did Uncle kill him?

00:19:12.039 --> 00:19:13.420
That man was a lunatic.

00:19:14.319 --> 00:19:15.900
He kidnapped me just for money.

00:19:16.039 --> 00:19:17.900
Uncle killed him to protect me.

00:19:18.319 --> 00:19:20.059
Don't worry about these things.

00:19:20.799 --> 00:19:23.400
Just focus on
preparing for going abroad.

00:19:23.819 --> 00:19:24.519
Alright?

00:19:30.039 --> 00:19:33.640
Uncle won't be released, right?

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:42.660
But Dad will be released, right?

00:19:48.200 --> 00:19:49.019
Yes.

00:19:51.539 --> 00:19:52.799
Your dad is innocent.

00:19:55.920 --> 00:19:57.180
Eighteen years.

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:01.559
Has it been that long?

00:20:01.920 --> 00:20:04.460
You were still in high school
back then, right?

00:20:05.519 --> 00:20:06.319
Tell me.

00:20:07.220 --> 00:20:09.559
How did you get involved
in the 6.10 case back then?

00:20:11.930 --> 00:20:14.700
(Beiyan County, Construction Site)

00:20:14.700 --> 00:20:15.640
Hurry! Come on!

00:20:15.640 --> 00:20:16.940
Let me see.

00:20:16.940 --> 00:20:17.940
Give me! Let me see!

00:20:39.799 --> 00:20:40.420
How is it?

00:20:41.180 --> 00:20:45.160
Can this thing even work?

00:20:46.200 --> 00:20:47.900
It can!

00:20:48.140 --> 00:20:50.900
They told me it'll work
once we load the gunpowder.

00:20:51.140 --> 00:20:52.279
It's in my pocket.

00:20:53.299 --> 00:20:54.460
But will it actually work?

00:20:55.640 --> 00:20:56.680
I haven't tested it.

00:20:56.720 --> 00:20:58.839
So will it work when the time comes?

00:21:00.420 --> 00:21:01.900
Wait, Dazhu. Won't we

00:21:01.900 --> 00:21:04.299
just use it to scare people
when we rob the credit union?

00:21:04.339 --> 00:21:05.640
Are we really going to shoot?

00:21:05.640 --> 00:21:06.700
Cut the crap.

00:21:07.059 --> 00:21:08.128
No, Dazhu.

00:21:08.128 --> 00:21:09.420
Leave it with me.

00:21:09.420 --> 00:21:09.940
Let's go.

00:21:11.079 --> 00:21:12.460
Enough talk.

00:21:12.640 --> 00:21:13.660
Leave it with me.

00:21:50.180 --> 00:21:52.059
Lijun, he's coughing up blood again.

00:21:56.299 --> 00:21:58.059
Lijun, how about this?

00:21:58.920 --> 00:22:00.700
I'll go buy some medicine

00:22:01.539 --> 00:22:03.180
or find a doctor to come over.

00:22:03.420 --> 00:22:04.319
Where to?

00:22:05.460 --> 00:22:06.920
The city is under a massive search.

00:22:07.559 --> 00:22:08.900
If you rush out like this

00:22:08.900 --> 00:22:10.920
and get caught, we'll all be done for.

00:22:11.420 --> 00:22:14.180
But I... I'm afraid...

00:22:14.799 --> 00:22:15.920
If we just do nothing,

00:22:17.299 --> 00:22:19.559
Yonghui won't make it.

00:22:21.720 --> 00:22:22.339
Yonghui.

00:22:23.700 --> 00:22:24.400
Lijun.

00:22:31.660 --> 00:22:32.299
I'll go.

00:22:32.960 --> 00:22:36.460
Dazhu, if I'm not back in two hours,

00:22:37.059 --> 00:22:39.799
tell Guangcai to move to
a different place with Yonghui.

00:22:40.928 --> 00:22:41.499
Lijun.

00:22:41.499 --> 00:22:42.440
What day is it?

00:22:44.539 --> 00:22:45.180
Yonghui.

00:22:46.559 --> 00:22:47.200
Yonghui.

00:22:47.339 --> 00:22:48.180
What did you say?

00:22:48.559 --> 00:22:51.920
What day is today?

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:54.200
The 11th.

00:22:55.059 --> 00:22:57.799
You've been injured
for a whole day since yesterday.

00:22:58.180 --> 00:22:59.140
How are you feeling?

00:23:00.799 --> 00:23:01.799
You can't go out.

00:23:02.660 --> 00:23:05.160
The police must be looking for us.

00:23:13.700 --> 00:23:15.220
When did your hand recover?

00:23:57.559 --> 00:23:59.400
(But about my left hand recovering,)

00:24:01.640 --> 00:24:02.839
no one knows.

00:24:04.920 --> 00:24:06.059
Not even my sister.

00:24:53.799 --> 00:24:55.779
(So everything that happened afterward)

00:24:57.680 --> 00:24:59.539
was entirely my idea.

00:25:02.339 --> 00:25:04.420
The first stab after your hand recovered

00:25:05.279 --> 00:25:07.180
wasn't against Huang Mantang, right?

00:25:10.170 --> 00:25:11.194
(Beiyan City, Urban Village)

00:25:20.400 --> 00:25:21.180
Xue Yonghui.

00:25:22.539 --> 00:25:24.839
I'm giving you another chance
to confess for leniency.

00:25:25.799 --> 00:25:29.839
How many people were involved
in the 6.10 case, and who were they?

00:25:32.700 --> 00:25:33.920
Five people in total.

00:25:35.279 --> 00:25:36.059
Me,

00:25:37.680 --> 00:25:38.559
Jiao Lijun,

00:25:40.940 --> 00:25:42.039
Wang Dazhu,

00:25:43.799 --> 00:25:45.039
Huang Mantang,

00:25:48.779 --> 00:25:50.559
and Zuo Long, who fired the gun.

00:25:55.839 --> 00:25:56.680
Xue Yonghui.

00:25:58.059 --> 00:25:59.328
Did Meng Guangcai order you

00:26:00.896 --> 00:26:02.420
to kill Huang Mantang?

00:26:05.440 --> 00:26:07.299
I decided to kill him myself.

00:26:11.539 --> 00:26:12.640
No one ordered it.

00:26:15.299 --> 00:26:16.680
That night at the hospital,

00:26:17.579 --> 00:26:20.799
the janitor who tried
to kill Lin Shan was you, right?

00:26:38.720 --> 00:26:39.680
Spit it out.

00:26:42.420 --> 00:26:43.160
Chief Liu.

00:26:44.420 --> 00:26:47.539
Today I won't call you Chief Liu.
You're Laoer of the Squad Nine.

00:26:51.680 --> 00:26:52.839
To be blunt,

00:26:55.059 --> 00:26:57.559
let me stay in the task force
for two more days.

00:26:59.339 --> 00:27:00.339
After two days,

00:27:02.640 --> 00:27:04.640
Meng Guangcai will be
released from our custody.

00:27:11.680 --> 00:27:14.680
I'm Laoda of the Squad Nine.

00:27:15.180 --> 00:27:16.799
But everyone knows

00:27:17.339 --> 00:27:19.299
you are more reliable than I am.

00:27:20.180 --> 00:27:22.940
Out of the four of us in Squad Nine,
only two and a half are left.

00:27:23.920 --> 00:27:26.299
I know it's all because of me,
and you resent me for it.

00:27:27.400 --> 00:27:29.660
Lin Shan's situation
is directly related to me.

00:27:30.940 --> 00:27:32.339
I'm the one who got Laosi killed.

00:27:33.799 --> 00:27:37.799
All these years, I've been completely
fooled by Xue Yonghui's prosthetic arm.

00:27:39.799 --> 00:27:42.200
I'm just stupid, blind, and bad.

00:27:44.299 --> 00:27:45.059
I know.

00:27:46.180 --> 00:27:49.140
All these years, you've never mentioned
Laosan and Laosi in front of me.

00:27:49.700 --> 00:27:51.079
I know you can't get over it.

00:27:52.420 --> 00:27:53.700
W-Who can get over it?

00:27:55.680 --> 00:27:57.180
We all call you Liu Unity.

00:27:57.920 --> 00:27:59.059
We all joked with you,

00:27:59.680 --> 00:28:01.920
saying you're suited
to be a chief and climb up.

00:28:01.920 --> 00:28:05.460
But we all know you're
extremely sentimental.

00:28:06.559 --> 00:28:10.259
Watching the buddies fall one by one
is like stabbing a knife into your heart.

00:28:11.220 --> 00:28:13.900
You assigned me to the kitchen,
and kicked me out of the task force.

00:28:15.420 --> 00:28:16.220
I understand.

00:28:19.559 --> 00:28:20.839
I have just one request today.

00:28:22.300 --> 00:28:23.539
Let me return to the task force

00:28:25.039 --> 00:28:26.299
and settle the case.

00:28:27.839 --> 00:28:28.799
No matter what,

00:28:30.700 --> 00:28:35.039
let me see this case through to the end.

00:28:35.960 --> 00:28:36.799
That's all.

00:28:40.779 --> 00:28:41.559
Done talking?

00:28:58.900 --> 00:29:00.339
I'm not in uniform today.

00:29:02.700 --> 00:29:03.920
I'm not Chief Liu today.

00:29:05.339 --> 00:29:07.680
I'm saying this as Liu Unity.

00:29:09.200 --> 00:29:10.839
With our experience,

00:29:12.299 --> 00:29:13.819
over these 18 years, Meng Guangcai

00:29:14.700 --> 00:29:15.920
has been preparing for today.

00:29:18.539 --> 00:29:21.299
He's managed to turn
the tables and escape.

00:29:23.440 --> 00:29:24.420
When the time comes,

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:27.400
we'll have to release him.

00:29:29.839 --> 00:29:31.279
Can you accept this?

00:29:33.039 --> 00:29:33.680
Zhu,

00:29:34.920 --> 00:29:36.799
look at what you've become now.

00:29:37.059 --> 00:29:38.039
See for yourself.

00:29:38.700 --> 00:29:40.559
How long haven't you looked in a mirror?

00:29:40.920 --> 00:29:42.019
Look at you.

00:29:43.140 --> 00:29:44.200
You're a mess.

00:29:47.039 --> 00:29:48.960
Don't you know your health?

00:29:51.339 --> 00:29:54.140
I don't want you to risk
your life on this one thing.

00:29:55.940 --> 00:29:58.799
We've already stripped everyone
around Meng Guangcai bare.

00:29:58.799 --> 00:30:00.400
That's already something.

00:30:00.559 --> 00:30:02.799
Why do you risk your life
on this single thing?

00:30:04.539 --> 00:30:05.940
Keep yourself healthy.

00:30:07.339 --> 00:30:11.559
We can keep fighting him, okay?

00:30:16.160 --> 00:30:17.079
But I...

00:30:18.700 --> 00:30:21.680
I can't just sit back
and watch him evade justice anymore.

00:30:21.680 --> 00:30:24.180
I can't let Laosan and Laosi's
grudges unsolved anymore.

00:30:24.339 --> 00:30:27.779
If so, I'd rather
give my own life for it.

00:30:28.059 --> 00:30:29.039
Is it helping anything?

00:30:34.940 --> 00:30:35.819
Is it useful?

00:30:38.559 --> 00:30:39.400
Zhu Helai.

00:30:40.839 --> 00:30:42.059
Look at me.

00:30:43.539 --> 00:30:44.799
What did you tell me before?

00:30:47.339 --> 00:30:48.700
Be loyal to hope.

00:30:49.700 --> 00:30:51.299
Loyal to justice and the law.

00:30:52.559 --> 00:30:53.400
What about now?

00:30:55.559 --> 00:30:57.299
Now you're loyal to an obsession.

00:31:00.860 --> 00:31:03.060
Only the two of us are left
from the four in Squad Nine.

00:31:04.180 --> 00:31:05.079
Laoda.

00:31:08.279 --> 00:31:09.019
Laoda.

00:31:13.960 --> 00:31:15.059
I mean, if...

00:31:18.299 --> 00:31:22.299
If one day, the two of us could go meet
Lin Shan and Du Ming together,

00:31:24.059 --> 00:31:25.559
that would be a pretty happy thing.

00:31:29.180 --> 00:31:31.299
I just don't want to be left alone,

00:31:32.400 --> 00:31:34.279
without anyone to drink with.

00:32:02.420 --> 00:32:03.819
Up to today, the 6.10 case

00:32:05.180 --> 00:32:07.059
is already very clear.

00:32:09.180 --> 00:32:11.960
Good! You finally solved the case.

00:32:12.299 --> 00:32:15.839
Jiao Lijun, Wang Dazhu, and Xue Yonghui.

00:32:16.460 --> 00:32:18.299
They have confessed to their crimes.

00:32:18.839 --> 00:32:20.400
They will face legal punishment.

00:32:21.279 --> 00:32:22.539
There's one thing

00:32:23.680 --> 00:32:25.180
I want to mention to you.

00:32:27.299 --> 00:32:28.779
The Huang Mantang you mentioned

00:32:29.839 --> 00:32:31.799
who was already dead.

00:32:33.799 --> 00:32:34.960
Now he really is dead.

00:32:42.559 --> 00:32:43.680
What do you want to say?

00:32:44.140 --> 00:32:45.299
During this long period,

00:32:48.600 --> 00:32:50.160
I've been interrogated again and again.

00:32:51.059 --> 00:32:53.019
Yet you have no witnesses
or physical evidence.

00:32:53.700 --> 00:32:55.559
Just based on Zhu Helai's
suspicion of me,

00:32:57.140 --> 00:32:58.680
you've kept me locked up until now.

00:32:58.920 --> 00:33:03.180
The first pre-IPO company in Beiyan
has been ruined in your hands.

00:33:04.839 --> 00:33:07.299
You can't justify this
to me, to my family,

00:33:07.920 --> 00:33:10.680
or to my company.

00:33:12.299 --> 00:33:13.460
You don't dare release me

00:33:14.960 --> 00:33:20.460
and insist on convicting me,
just to close this case, right?

00:33:33.440 --> 00:33:38.140
Uncle, you're settled up
with Caisheng Group.

00:33:41.680 --> 00:33:44.160
He got off cheap with
just that little bit of money.

00:33:45.400 --> 00:33:46.590
If it weren't for me,

00:33:47.168 --> 00:33:50.160
a country boy like Meng Guangcai
could never make it this far.

00:33:53.640 --> 00:33:55.839
Just stop being foolish.

00:33:55.839 --> 00:33:58.200
If you'd listened to my advice
and cut ties with him,

00:33:58.559 --> 00:34:00.779
we could've taken the money and escaped.

00:34:00.920 --> 00:34:02.559
We wouldn't have ended up like this.

00:34:03.160 --> 00:34:05.400
Do you think
Meng Guangcai really loves you?

00:34:05.400 --> 00:34:08.219
He kept you in the company
to get close to me.

00:34:08.780 --> 00:34:11.340
And what did you do?
At such a young age, you just...

00:34:11.780 --> 00:34:13.300
You just had a child.

00:34:13.780 --> 00:34:15.300
She's just a burden to you now.

00:34:18.800 --> 00:34:20.059
My dad died young,

00:34:21.119 --> 00:34:24.199
so I could only follow my mom
and become someone else's daughter.

00:34:25.880 --> 00:34:27.420
I never had a choice.

00:34:30.360 --> 00:34:34.039
Uncle, you were like a father
to me, choosing my school,

00:34:34.699 --> 00:34:37.179
and choosing Caisheng Group
for me after graduation.

00:34:37.699 --> 00:34:41.059
You told me to keep an eye on
Meng Guangcai. I did all that.

00:34:42.960 --> 00:34:45.820
Being with Meng Guangcai was a mistake.

00:34:46.199 --> 00:34:48.380
I shouldn't have interfered
in someone else's life.

00:34:50.079 --> 00:34:51.500
But you all got it wrong.

00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:54.139
I was never after Meng Guangcai's money.

00:34:54.380 --> 00:34:56.059
I never had any grand illusions either.

00:34:56.420 --> 00:34:58.579
In my whole life,
I've always been told what to do.

00:34:58.579 --> 00:35:02.000
Only Chuchu. I chose
to give birth to her.

00:35:03.880 --> 00:35:05.719
She's never a burden to me.

00:35:07.159 --> 00:35:08.400
She is my daughter.

00:35:23.579 --> 00:35:24.360
Fine.

00:35:25.760 --> 00:35:28.760
You choose your path,
and I'll choose mine.

00:36:27.179 --> 00:36:30.260
Mr. Xie, where are you going?

00:36:36.219 --> 00:36:37.360
I'm not going anywhere.

00:36:37.500 --> 00:36:40.159
I just ate too much dinner,
and came out for a stroll.

00:36:41.019 --> 00:36:41.780
A stroll?

00:36:46.920 --> 00:36:49.880
Carrying that much money?
Where exactly are you strolling to?

00:36:52.019 --> 00:36:54.719
Come on. Let's go have a chat.

00:37:01.280 --> 00:37:02.719
(Up to today, the 6.10 case)

00:37:03.179 --> 00:37:06.719
Jiao Lijun, Wang Dazhu, and Xue Yonghui.

00:37:07.360 --> 00:37:09.219
They have confessed to their crimes.

00:37:09.760 --> 00:37:11.179
(They will face legal punishment.)

00:37:32.519 --> 00:37:34.460
(That Huang Mantang
who was already dead.)

00:37:37.500 --> 00:37:38.619
(Now he really is dead.)

00:37:56.420 --> 00:37:57.179
Xiaoliang.

00:37:58.420 --> 00:38:02.000
Tomorrow morning,
come with me to pick up Dad, okay?

00:38:06.042 --> 00:38:11.488
(Beiyan Central Hospital)

00:38:17.780 --> 00:38:18.500
Laosan.

00:38:21.360 --> 00:38:23.119
This time, I might really lose.

00:38:52.680 --> 00:38:57.704
=The Silent Rift=